cff-version: 1.2.0
title: AgentFlow
message: "If you use this software, please cite the accompanying paper (preferred-citation block below)."
abstract: >-
  AgentFlow is a multi-agent framework for enterprise API orchestration that
  learns three runtime parameters online: routing weights via a gradient-free
  optimizer, circuit-breaker cooldown via an MDP-formalized multiplicative-weight
  policy, and intent-parser selection via a confidence-thresholded hybrid parser.
  The framework is released open source under the Apache 2.0 license.
type: software
